---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Room of Wires - Fragile Melodic Moments">
  <main>
    <div
      class="h-screen bg-cover bg-no-repeat bg-fixed bg-center bg-[url('/images/dasf.jpg')]"
    >
      <div
        class="h-full flex items-center justify-center text-gray-200 font-sans"
      >
        <div class="text-left mx-12 w-[80%] h-[80%] md:h-[60%]">
          <div class="w-[95%] md:w-[50%] p-4">
            <img src="/images/dasf-logo.png" alt="DasF logo" class="h-10" />
            <p class="pt-4">
              DasF is the meeting of The Dronefynder General and the Andrews
              from Room of Wires, in a deep connection of time and sound.
            </p>
            <p class="pt-2">
              Creating dark, urgent and unsettling electronica, forged from
              evaporating melodies and throbbing layers of sonic disquiet.
            </p>
            <p class="pt-2">
              Anonymous found fragments from passing encounters and urban
              moments are weaved with deep oscillations. Half memories... the
              fleeting unfolding of themes and sound spaces. Darkness with
              occasional chinks of light. Welcome to DasF.
            </p>
            <p class="pt-2">
              New 4-track EP Bordata is out now on Rednetic Records.
            </p>
            <p class="pt-2">
              Debut EP <a
                href="https://section27.bandcamp.com/album/trenchcoat-ep"
                target="_blank"
                class="text-gray-100 font-bold">Trenchcoat</a
              > - Section 27.
            </p>
            <div
              class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-3 pt-8"
            >
              <div class="aspect-w-1 aspect-h-1">
                <a
                  href="https://rednetic.bandcamp.com/album/bordata-ep"
                  target="_blank"
                >
                  <img
                    src="/images/DasF_bordata_cover.jpg"
                    alt="DasF Bordata cover"
                    class="object-cover"
                  /></a
                >
              </div>
              <div class="aspect-w-1 aspect-h-1">
                <a
                  href="https://section27.bandcamp.com/album/trenchcoat-ep"
                  target="_blank"
                >
                  <img
                    src="/images/trenchcoat_ep.jpg"
                    alt="Trenchcoat cover"
                    class="object-cover"
                  /></a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm pt-8">
              <a href="/latest">[ go to roomofwires.com ]</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
